  "description": "Mistral Large 3 (675B Instruct 2512 NVFP4) is a state-of-the-art general-purpose Multimodal granular Mixture-of-Experts model with 41B active parameters and 675B total parameters trained from scratch with 3000 H200s. This model is the instruct post-trained version, fine-tuned for instruction tasks, making it ideal for chat, agentic and instruction based use cases. This is a high quality NVFP4 version to reduce resource requirements. Can be deployed on a node of H100s or A100s.\n\nDesigned for reliability and long-context comprehension - It is engineered for production-grade assistants, retrieval-augmented systems, scientific workloads, and complex enterprise workflows.",
